Achievements.Name: Naval Academy Graduation
Achievements.Description: Complete all Naval Academy missions

Achievements.Name: Veteran of Midway
Achievements.Description: Complete all Single Player missions

Achievements.Name: Hardened Veteran of Midway
Achievements.Description: Complete all Single Player missions on Veteran difficulty level

Achievements.Name: Veteran Pilot
Achievements.Description: Complete all Plane Challenge missions

Achievements.Name: Veteran Captain
Achievements.Description: Complete all Ship Challenge missions

Achievements.Name: Veteran Submarine Commander
Achievements.Description: Complete all Submarine Challenge missions

Achievements.Name: Submarine Service Medal
Achievements.Description: At least 15 minutes unit usage plus used this unit type the most in the mission

Achievements.Name: Air Unit Service Medal
Achievements.Description: At least 20 minutes unit usage plus used this unit type the most in the mission

Achievements.Name: Sea Unit Service Medal
Achievements.Description: At least 25 minutes unit usage plus used this unit type the most in the mission

Achievements.Name: Torpedo Marksmanship
Achievements.Description: Achieve 15 torpedo hits as well as most torpedo hits in mission

Achievements.Name: AA Marksmanship
Achievements.Description: Achieve 100 AA hits as well as most AA hits in mission

Achievements.Name: Artillery Marksmanship
Achievements.Description: Achieve 200 Artillery hits as well as most Artillery hits in mission

Achievements.Name: Legion of Merit
Achievements.Description: Team Kill/Death ratio must be at least 5:1

Achievements.Name: Bronze Star
Achievements.Description: Team Kill/Death ratio must be at least 3:1

Achievements.Name: Purple Heart
Achievements.Description: Worst Kill/Death ratio amongst the Players

Achievements.Name: Distinguished Service Cross
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemy planes and 10 enemy ships

Achievements.Name: Silver Star
Achievements.Description: Kill 10 enemy planes and 5 enemy ships

Achievements.Name: Navy Cross
Achievements.Description: Kill 10 enemy ships and reach at least 5 min ship usage

Achievements.Name: Navy Distinguished Service Medal
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 enemy ships and reach at least 5 min ship usage

Achievements.Name: Distinguished Flying Cross
Achievements.Description: Kill 40 enemy planes and reach at least 5 min plane usage

Achievements.Name: Air Medal
Achievements.Description: Kill 20 enemy planes and reach at least 5 min plane usage

Achievements.Name: Medal of Honor
Achievements.Description: Must reach the time and hit limits of the Service and the Marksmanship medals
